{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 965218, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 195544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "因为现在拜登经费到账了。你看看去年有没有这样的事？", "timestamp": 1611364187, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 965221, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 195544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "真信脱贫攻坚吗？ 到基层完全变味了", "timestamp": 1611364237, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 965236, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 195544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "？dz再看看所谓的扶贫政策吧，实操中很多不到被扶贫标准但生活艰巨的例子", "timestamp": 1611364420, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 965237, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 195544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "#政治相关", "timestamp": 1611364491, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 965238, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 195544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "脱贫攻坚基本是个面子工程，dz到贫困地区看看就知道了", "timestamp": 1611364508, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 965242, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 195544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我将无我，不负人民", "timestamp": 1611364584, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 965261, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 195544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果没有脱贫攻坚，这样死的人要多几千倍你信不信？他看不起病做不起手术的根本原因到底是资本主义还是社会主义？", "timestamp": 1611365012, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 965263, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 195544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 非我也，美利坚也", "timestamp": 1611365030, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 965306, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 195544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "脱贫攻坚是织一张网，需要大量艰苦的实际工作。落到实际中，总会有这样那样的漏洞。但总比什么都不做强。", "timestamp": 1611365843, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 965377, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 195544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "脱贫攻坚本来就没那么美好", "timestamp": 1611366850, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 965384, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 195544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "在我看来国家精准扶贫做的已经很好了，我前几天回农村，政府帮盖不起房的盖房子，帮没生计的找事做，只要不好吃懒做，都能过的不错的，这些都是村民自己说的（仅限我见到的，并非指墨茶好吃懒做）", "timestamp": 1611366999, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 965420, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 195544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "同意Hans，扶贫比不扶贫好，虽然扶贫工作自上而下推行中有若干问题，但远比不扶贫好。此外即使现在宣布全面建成小康社会了，扶贫仍然不能停止，不然很多地方会返贫……", "timestamp": 1611367599, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 965435, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 195544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "墨茶说明的不是脱贫攻坚没用，是脱贫攻坚有用但做得还不够。说实话，刚刚脱离绝对贫困满足温饱的水平，够干啥的？所以还要乡村振兴再干很多年....", "timestamp": 1611367719, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 965583, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 195544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "好像有博主去了解墨茶家去了，貌似家境还是挺不错的，他母亲说给墨茶打电话联系墨茶也不回复。可能从墨茶母亲的角度看更是网瘾少年离家出走了无音信，从墨茶的角度看是家人不管不顾不闻不问。", "timestamp": 1611368857, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 965606, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 3967, "w": 690}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 195544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "", "timestamp": 1611369059, "type": "image", "url": "z5/z5qsdcf6r7q43vtuqyfisgft5zyetajn.jpeg"}, {"cid": 965871, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 195544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我打个？，不懂别瞎说求求了，我老爸是扶贫干部，管理两年在贫困县，干了太多实事儿，你这样说真的让人很心寒", "timestamp": 1611371094, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 965873, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 195544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 不好意思真的不是面子工程，每年都去我爸扶贫的村子，变化翻天覆地，谢谢\n", "timestamp": 1611371138, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 966371, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 195544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Margaret: 我只想说…中国很大……", "timestamp": 1611373981, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 968237, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Olivia", "pid": 195544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 哪怕这篇文章有预设立场和故意引导之嫌，依然可以看出他母亲是什么人，“职高肄业”说得那么轻巧，难道不是因病致贫被迫辍学？既然条件不错为什么不给孩子资助让他读完高中拿到文凭？孩子为什么不愿意理自己这个母亲心里没点数吗？然后把他定性为孤僻网瘾少年？这文读得我简直生理不适", "timestamp": 1611388581, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 968250, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Olivia", "pid": 195544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Olivia: 当然，这些感想是在假定b站上流传的墨茶生平为真的前提下，也可能我先入为主视角偏狭了，但总之我还是很生气", "timestamp": 1611388634, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 968481, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Olivia", "pid": 195544, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Olivia: 突然反应过来记者可能是在春秋笔法，确实不算是脱贫工作不到位的锅，而这个家庭问题极大。总之这个母亲令人不适。", "timestamp": 1611390401, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 11, "pid": 195544, "reply": 21, "tag": null, "text": "为啥四川凉山还存在 墨茶Official 这样贫困致死的人，脱贫攻坚的时候没有对这些人进行扶助吗？", "timestamp": 1611364136, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1611390398, "url": "", "vote": {}}}